        <updateDate>2023-03-24T01:48:19Z</updateDate>
        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Abandoned Well Remediation Research and Development Act&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This bill requires the Department of Energy (DOE) to establish a research, development, and demonstration program concerning abandoned oil and gas wells. Under the program, DOE must work to improve (1) data collection on the location of abandoned oil or gas wells; (2) the plugging, remediation, reclamation, and repurposing of the wells; and (3) strategies to mitigate potential environmental impacts of documented and undocumented abandoned wells.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
